title: Supreme Court decides against allowing appeal by Conor McGregor over Nikita Hand ruling
description: The decision has been welcomed by the Dublin Rape Crisis Centre.
content:
THE SUPREME COURT has decided it will not allow a further appeal by Conor McGregor against findings that he had sexually assaulted Nikita Hand.
